    <p> Welcome to the course.</p>


  <paragraphs>
    <title>Course Information</title>
    <p>
      This course introduces students to the foundations of discrete mathematics. The topics of study include 
      propositional logic, methods of proof, set theory, relations and functions, mathematical induction and recursion, 
      and elementary combinators.
    </p>
  </paragraphs>

  <paragraphs xml:id="sec-grading">
    <title>Grading</title>
    <p>This course has no grades because it is just a demo.</p>
  </paragraphs>

